Class ArrayIterable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.util.collect.ArrayIterable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>

    public class ArrayIterable<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<T>
    Iterable of an array object that does not make a copy of the array.

    Designed to be used when it is too expensive to copy an array to a List and use the list as an Iterable instead.
